---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Medical Marijuana Card near Riverview and Valrico | Releaf MD" 
  description="Get certified for a medical marijuana card if you live in Riverview, Valrico, or surrounding areas. Clinical evaluations by Dr. Kelly Ennix King."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        📍 Riverview & Valrico Services
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase">Medical Marijuana Card Riverview & Valrico</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Clinical evaluations and card services for Valrico and Riverview residents. Trusted guidance from Dr. Kelly Ennix King.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Local Medical Marijuana Evaluations</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          If you are searching for a convenient way to get your medical marijuana card in Riverview or Valrico, FL, Releaf MD offers personalized clinical care nearby. Our clinic is led by Dr. Kelly Ennix King, an experienced physician who helps patients understand the state certification process, dosing guidelines, and dispensary products.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Serving East Hillsborough County</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          We welcome patients from throughout the Riverview, Valrico, FishHawk, and Lithia areas. Our goal is to make the evaluation process stress-free and efficient. During your private consultation, Dr. Kelly will review your medical records, perform the required physical assessment, and discuss your therapeutic goals.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Office Location</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-700 font-bold mb-1">
              📍 935 Oakfield Dr. Brandon, FL 33511
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Conveniently located in Brandon, easily accessible from US-301, I-75, and SR-60 for Valrico and Riverview residents.
            </p>
            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=935+Oakfield+Dr+Brandon+FL+33511" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block mt-2 text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary hover:underline">Get Directions &rarr;</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Hours of Operation</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              <strong>Monday &ndash; Friday:</strong> 9 AM &ndash; 4 PM<br/>
              <strong>Saturday &ndash; Sunday:</strong> Closed<br/>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1 block">(Hours may differ on public holidays)</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-mint/20 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 my-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Looking for a Brandon Doctor?</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            We also have detailed information and local services tailored to our neighbors in <a href="/locations/brandon" class="text-brand-accent font-bold hover:underline">Brandon, FL</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Getting Certified: The State Process</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          To obtain your active card, you will need to complete three simple milestones:
        </p>

        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Consultation:</strong> Meet with Dr. Kelly for your required in-person evaluation.</li>
          <li><strong>Registry Registration:</strong> Log into the Florida OMMU registry portal to upload your proof of residency and payment.</li>
          <li><strong>Dispensary Access:</strong> Once the state approves your digital application (usually in 5-10 business days), you can purchase medical cannabis immediately.</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 my-8 text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
          Need a step-by-step breakdown? Read our comprehensive overview on our <a href="/evaluations" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Evaluations Page</a>.
        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
            Read our <a href="/florida-medical-marijuana-card-guide" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Complete Florida Card Guide</a>.
          </p>
          <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing/online-scheduling?service=xnfeicu6jent0179" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
            Schedule Appointment
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
